{
  "texts": [
    "• Platform design and business models can influence user behavior (Carmi et al. 2020).",
    "Thus, promoting data thinking could be a valuable extension to the dimension of awareness in a datafied environment.",
    "Additionally, data thinking also includes aspects of critical usage of data such as the ability to critically consider and discuss data analysis and communication (Yates et al. 2021), which makes it relevant for the dimensions of reflection and empowerment and overlaps with the aspects of data doing and data participation.",
    "In a data-driven debate, critical reflection on and active positioning in relation to content can necessitate thinking about and engaging with the underlying data.",
    "Along with data thinking, literacy skills in actively engaging with data (data doing) (Carmi et al. 2020; Yates et al. 2020) may be essential to the dimension of reflection and empowerment."
  ]
}